      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, garage-kept and pampered every single day. If you\u2019re looking for a smooth, flawless ride that\u2019s basically brand new, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to a great home! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
